<ITEM><HI>Pro&s;titution,</HI> and a promi&s;cuous u&s;e of <HI>women</HI> promoted by <HI>Satan,</HI> as a &s;acred rite among&s;t the heathens, and why, 159, et &s;eq.</ITEM>
<ITEM><HI>P&s;alm</HI> cii. Something peculiarly deep and my&s;terious there|in, 266 n.</ITEM>
<ITEM><PB N="437" REF="438"><HI>Puffendorff.</HI> A po&s;ition of his examined, 69, et &s;eq. Has well defended the general rule of <HI>Doing as we would be done by,</HI> again&s;t Dr. Sharrock, 70.</ITEM>
