<ITEM><HI>Spirit.</HI> See <HI>Holy Gho&s;t.</HI></ITEM>
<ITEM><HI>Spirits</HI>&mdash;may conver&s;e with us by &s;ecret illap&s;es without our perception, 118 n. See <HI>Enemies (Spiritual) Satan, Devil, Demon, Evil Spirits.</HI></ITEM>
