<ITEM><HI>Turks.</HI> See <HI>Arabians,</HI> &amp;c.</ITEM>
<ITEM><HI>Tyrants.</HI> It is nece&s;&s;ary for them, either to <HI>mi&s;repre&s;ent,</HI> or to <HI>deny</HI> the <HI>law of nature,</HI> 5. See <HI>Thomp&s;on.</HI></ITEM>
